Job Description &amp; Requirements

  Assembly of higher end products which require self-interpretation and understanding of technical drawing, assembly requirements, which also includes Geometric Dimensioning and Tolerance
  Electrical wiring and soldering for installation and assembling of mechanical and sub-assembly level components.
  Troubleshooting of machinery, servicing and maintenance.
  Perform testing and commissioning of machines and testers.
  Providing smooth and continuous running and support on machines and projects.
  To provide rework or make call for the required rework processes.
  Providing guidance to the team of operators.

Competence Requirements

  Preferred to have Secondary / NTC / Diploma in engineering field or equivalent.
  Fresh NTC / Diploma holder may be considered, else others with minimum 3 years of related work experience in manufacturing environment.
  Able to read and interpret technical drawing.
